{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she often thought of that when the bombers were up there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And remember what I had said, I don't want to get bombed by American bombers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gradually got home on the last day of the World's Fair in October 30.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father and my brothers picked me up and back to a normal world, and.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the people I left behind, I left in a very tragic situation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before we go any further, I'd like to ask you, what did you know about the concentration camps while you were still in Germany?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How much did you actually know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler didn't spread that around too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even the people involved were perhaps not too proud of it, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was knowable, excepting that I had practically no German, and we also had practically no time to read the newspapers or anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- the students, primarily Jewish people that made this such a successful school with their desire to learn English, and other languages too, French or-- or Spanish, for Latin America.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't say much about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you wouldn't like what he told me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are we on duty here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, the Jews didn't behave so well, he said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] He, of course, was a professional non-Jew, the poor man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you that not only did he regard himself as not a Jew, the poor, unfortunate man, but he also was very puzzled that his church, so-called church, the Lutheran church, when he went to the different helpful committees in Berlin, would have nothing to do with him.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't go to the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
